<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Скачать приложение Pixel Project</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Press+Start+2P&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Press Start 2P', monospace;
            background: #2a1a3a;
            color: #fff;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            flex-direction: column;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            background: #1e2538;
            border: 3px solid #ffaa66;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 40px;
            max-width: 500px;
            width: 100%;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #ffaa66;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
        .icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            line-height: 2;
            color: #aaa;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .download-btn {
            background: #3a6a4a;
            border: none;
            font-family: inherit;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            color: #fff;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 4px 4px 0 #1a4a2a;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            display: inline-block;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: 0.2s;
        }
        .download-btn:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }
        .back-btn {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 0.5rem;
            color: #ffaa66;
            text-decoration: underline;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-family: inherit;
            background: none;
            border: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="icon">🎲</div>
        <h1>PIXEL PROJECT</h1>
        <p>Установи наше приложение на телефон.<br>Бронируй игры, общайся в чате и получай скидки прямо с главного экрана!</p>
        <a href="/pixel-project.apk" class="download-btn" download>📲 СКАЧАТЬ APK</a>
        <button class="back-btn" onclick="window.location.href='/'">← Вернуться на сайт</button>
    </div>
</body>
</html>